    <description>Klingon Armada is an official conversion of the Star Fleet Universe to the Starmada rules. Players can fight one-on-one duels, but Klingon Armada is particularly suited for fleet engagements. The rules are simple, but not simplistic.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn, players simultaneously write orders for all of their ships, and then the orders are executed in turn order. The mechanics for combat are simple, but there is large amount of variety in the weapon effects. Ships lose effectiveness from damage until they are expanding clouds of debris.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Klingon Armada can be played with miniatures or counters from the Federation Commander series.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This book includes quick-start rules and 40 starship diagrams (from Klingon Border and Klingon Attack).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Additional books with more starships are planned.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Integrates with:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Starmada: The Admiralty Edition&amp;#10;    Romulan Armada&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
